{"tid":42672,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[處女之作•改詞]矮仔情深 (原曲:六天-周柏豪)","createTime":"2016-12-17T01:22:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-12T07:08:41.000Z","uid":17813,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"4f43714b38136c2b3fe5674cdbc32f9137e33c25","tid":42672,"uid":17813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T01:22:16.000Z","msg":"大家幫手畀啲意見，呢首係小弟第一次改嘅歌，裏面包含住我嘅個人感情，所以每粒字都係有感情喺裏面嘅！<br />\n<br />\n矮仔情深<br />\n夢想 有天 共妳 一起<br />\n我裝 傻氣 與妳 有好天氣  <br />\n我竟 仍然苦掛念妳 不管能否一起<br />\n可笑 是我仍為你顧忌<br />\n每到聖誕 望共她於沙灘<br />\n觀看星空不孤單<br />\n最凍那晚 夢想可跟她擁抱著...渡過...今晚 會嗎?<br />\n<br />\n＊情人沒我份 孤身抹去淚痕 我慣了單身<br />\n祗想抱願去等 悲痛難堪 祗想可增高半分<br />\n仍然為妳等<br />\n孤單 獨斷獨行想call你都手震<br />\n盼望我能與妳 祗想有 一 天 可<br />\nMarry with you........<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我悄悄說 在最初識她不夠膽幻想 可高攀<br />\n但我身高卻跟她 擁有著段距就 不揀 我嗎?<br />\n<br />\n＊情人沒我份 孤身抹去淚痕 我慣了單身<br />\n祗想抱願去等 悲痛難堪 祗想可增高半分<br />\n仍然為妳等<br />\n祗想 你會回頭 給我獻出一吻<br />\n盼望妳能共我 可會有 一 天 我<br />\nMarry with you........<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n為何無論妳到哪裡 得妳永在我心<br />\n能否搞清楚 這個眼前人是我<br />\n你會動情麼?<br />\n<br />\n仍然沒我份 傷心滿面淚痕 每晚上高登<br />\n叫春我亦有感 一往情深 祗想可跟她結婚<br />\n仍然為愛等<br />\n珍惜這眼前人 洗清妳的心癮<br />\n盼望妳能共我 可以令這一生 永遠合襯<br />\n或許 我心 就算 比他 更好<br />\n仍不 令妳 與我共舞"},{"pid":"eaaeb74588667494156294b66232645243136a93","tid":42672,"uid":17813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T01:25:03.000Z","msg":"首詞11月中嗰陣寫，當時未有連登，所以不喜勿屌"},{"pid":"f0c8fa3f1ade9fa8ebbf2c284b15e611e81358e4","tid":42672,"uid":48404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T02:09:27.000Z","msg":"你自己有冇試過唱出黎？"},{"pid":"55a63d9824e952acbae4a449e2399e43845850c6","tid":42672,"uid":1779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T02:11:43.000Z","msg":"好多唔啱音喎哥仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5e96c86f77136a3271746ec7f7978821236669c","tid":42672,"uid":17813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T02:27:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你自己有冇試過唱出黎？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有，不過我唱得好難聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"547d3c135e73c441c6efb9b53f644645b11646a9","tid":42672,"uid":17813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T02:34:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好多唔啱音喎哥仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n邊啲位唔啱音？"},{"pid":"4ae77e9f06a8559de7066694b9d32f6e5eddf165","tid":42672,"uid":48143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T03:05:13.000Z","msg":"痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你認真架？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好低質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b23743d16a0b248ba6fcfef253e74fec7f4c6e3","tid":42672,"uid":12471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T03:47:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>好多唔啱音喎哥仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n邊啲位唔啱音？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n大部你有改既字都唔啱音<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"531040da71ceb85d916195ea6d4f3d8afde382da","tid":42672,"uid":12471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T03:48:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>好多唔啱音喎哥仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n邊啲位唔啱音？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n大部你有改既字都唔啱音<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n大部<span style=\"color: red;\">分</span>你有改既字都唔啱音<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />[/quote]"},{"pid":"d1707a93492a018d10c2358cc4020e3edff361b1","tid":42672,"uid":48143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T03:54:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n邊啲位唔啱音？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n大部你有改既字都唔啱音<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n大部<span style=\"color: red;\">份</span>你有改既字都唔啱音<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>[/quote]<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"076b866a1b58d3e19b237c56f6cbc53be1e1fe5d","tid":42672,"uid":48498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T03:56:21.000Z","msg":"其實你都無乜改到，有改嘅就好格硬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n下次試下唔好唔好跟住原詞改，跟音樂改同唔好用原詞字眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64fd8a99a208970c3ea30b658c40d458114df651","tid":42672,"uid":48498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T03:59:40.000Z","msg":"依首我係改詞post都有改過，都唔係改得好，但係你可以參考下<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>六天果度仲係未得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n多憂<span style=\"color: red;\">心</span>似亂麻<br />\n會變左滲透個滲</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"http://vocaroo.com/i/s1skyGveqx9x\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvocaroo.com%2Fi%2Fs1skyGveqx9x&d=NhYFn%2Fa2OU0mLL9Pl%2FauMnvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=45cae60a\" target=\"_blank\">http://vocaroo.com/i/s1skyGveqx9x</a>[/quote]<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />[/quote]<br />\n<br />\n我都係覺得唔得[/quote]<br />\n<br />\n《樹蛙》<br />\n原曲：六天<br />\n新詞：大豬包包<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">聽</span>這 樹蛙 說那 初夏<br />\n與他 回家 事發 太過不雅<br />\n再聽 為何他撇下嗎 不想著這瘡疤 <br />\n驚怕 謝謝我共你談話<br />\n<br />\n那聖誕假 另有新歡的她<br />\n剩下我獨個等開花<br />\n我這洞裡 <span style=\"color: pink;\">天天</span>堆積她幾百萬句 心聲細沙<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">細聽</span>樹裏蛙 <span style=\"color: teal;\">憂心滲似</span>亂麻<br />\n我故作啞巴 你總掛念某他 <span style=\"color: pink;\">多處成家</span><br />\n可否親暱得似他<br />\n柳暗淚正灑 花香襯托月明 心不配怎招架<br />\n我告白如亂碼 這個<span style=\"color: blue;\">洞 窟</span> <span style=\"color: pink;\">不敢替你護駕</span><br />\n<br />\n我聽你讚頌我多麽好 一輩子永不可找到<br />\n笑說我愛著你 怎麼可找到伴侶 這可算糟？<br />\n<br />\n無人明白柳暗處處 怎去也是會輸<br />\n無花開天光 心卻似<span style=\"color: green;\">鍛鐵</span>煉鋼 作 半日良方<br />\n<br />\n快要下雪花 曉江雪似亂麻<br />\n斷節嚇鷗鴉 免得你淚再灑 冬柳無花 <br />\n霜風他抵得了嗎<br />\n柳暗淚正灑 枯萎襯托月明<br />\n可不聽他欺詐 我告白如亂碼 這個<span style=\"color: blue;\">洞 窟</span>不敢<span style=\"color: pink;\">替你護駕</span><br />\n<br />\n又到 夏至 靜聽 新的 正史<br />\n明知 又會 再有下次<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有時間嘅錄埋個Demo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n原本想打文案，不過大家睇唔明再問我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 最後引用左少少《冬柳》依首詩<br />\n男主角係柳樹，女主角係樹蛙，大家可以睇下係柳樹角度下單戀依隻樹蛙嘅故事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n獻醜了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />[/quote]<br />\n<br />\n加油"},{"pid":"af556eb2cbc0acd8485f98d11bde9f038f4056ab","tid":42672,"uid":15323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T04:01:50.000Z","msg":"好多位唔岩音<br />\n可以參考林夕點寫押韻<br />\n有d轉折位意思唔係好通"},{"pid":"645bd7ea50896763037854bbf17921af6873a537","tid":42672,"uid":1779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T06:50:44.000Z","msg":"樓上嗰首仲夾硬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5170cd3f706b9714bf6e8e322a269146e0dbac1b","tid":42672,"uid":65175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T17:30:52.000Z","msg":"Marry &ldquo;with&rdquo; you 係錯grammar. marry you 就得。"},{"pid":"f91fb301b40502d8f7f90ff2904c328afe33cb19","tid":42672,"uid":41326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T23:24:15.000Z","msg":"留個靚名天氣放晴"},{"pid":"1d6338d0e7138b835b91064f027f99aeba2df3ce","tid":42672,"uid":17813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T12:59:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquo